## ğŸ§© 2ï¸âƒ£ Service Container (IoC) â€” *â€œWhat is the Service Container?â€*

**Theory:**
Itâ€™s Laravelâ€™s **dependency injection system** â€” it automatically provides class dependencies when needed.
