## ğŸ§± 3ï¸âƒ£ Service Providers â€” *â€œWhat are they for?â€*

**Theory:**
Theyâ€™re the **bootstrappers** of Laravel. Everything â€” routing, events, validation â€” is registered via service providers.

**Real-world example:**
