## ğŸ§® 5ï¸âƒ£ Eloquent ORM â€” *â€œWhy Eloquent is powerful?â€*

**Theory:**
Eloquent is Laravelâ€™s **ActiveRecord ORM**, allowing object-based database interaction.
It maps models directly to DB tables.

**Real-world example:**

```php
