## âš™ï¸ 8ï¸âƒ£ RouteServiceProvider â€” *â€œWhat is its role?â€*

**Theory:**
It tells Laravel **where to load routes** from (`web.php`, `api.php`) and **defines route model binding behavior.**

**Real-world example:**
Inside `RouteServiceProvider`, you can define:

```php
