## ğŸ“¤ 12ï¸âƒ£ Queues & Jobs â€” *â€œWhen should you use queues?â€*

**Theory:**
For long-running tasks â€” email sending, image processing, notifications.
Laravel queues offload those to background workers.

**Real-world example:**

```bash
